{"tid":1375362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請你地回憶起初心，不分化，不割席，不譴責。","createTime":"2019-07-28T04:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T05:29:56.000Z","uid":17607,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"869b18aac3e494a129e4defee6cc957a059a35f8","tid":1375362,"uid":17607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:50:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">老老實實，我覺得呢家真係多左好多鬼係連登。<br />\n<br />\n不斷開post屌各位，咩都屌，屌youtuber，屌和理非，屌勇武。<br />\n<br />\n請大家諗返起我地成個運動既初心<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>不分化，不割席，不譴責</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n各位，無論你係和理非，物資，勇武，我地真係缺一不可，大家係靠合作，互相理解先可以去到今日既位置。<br />\n<br />\n所有野都係前線決線，勇武係前面檔，保護後面既人，佢地付出既野係好多好多，請大家尊重佢地。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"8c9b6e5929a5ba030e5d81b9653546d87d117fb1","tid":1375362,"uid":17607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:51:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55fad4d3cc31397e4d310f41a69be7e2d2a1146c","tid":1375362,"uid":166777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:51:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"268d9e656d133cec9713674850c171544a4dbb0a","tid":1375362,"uid":17607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:52:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d40dafc21aed52d800d5346b7fe43a4fda84fac6","tid":1375362,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:52:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a0b03089769c9e232516b89444db8fe2109b00b","tid":1375362,"uid":221919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:53:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208f1a1a756715765b91d807fbbedfb1d678861a","tid":1375362,"uid":17607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T